com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-lilith-operator-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-lilith-operator-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-warzone"><em>《使命召唤：战区》</em></a> <a href="https://www.callofduty.com/blog/2023/09/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-II-warzone-season-06-haunting-multiplayer-modes-zombies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第 6 季</a>以 The Haunting 为特色，它将通过游戏模式和新的可玩干员链接到<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/diablo-4"><em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em></a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/the-mountain-goats-john-darnielle-talks-magic-the-gathering-secret-lair-set-3483851">山羊乐队的约翰·达尼尔 (John Darnielle) 谈论为《万智牌》写预言</a></strong></li></ul><p>作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/call-of-duty-modern-warfare-3"><em>《使命召唤：现代战争 3》</em></a>发布之前上线的最后一季，动视将在第六季的时间表中为《战区》社区提供大量万圣节主题内容。</p><p>噩梦行动将在阿尔马兹拉的夜间进行，让玩家对抗从热点地区出现的可怕异常现象。然后，《Vondead》预计将发生在冯德尔的血月下，导致僵尸爆发。</p><p>前一种模式将根据消灭最想要的目标来奖励玩家独家奖励，而后一种模式则与<em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em>的屠夫联系在一起，因为敌人会从地图上的恶魔祭坛吸取力量。 </p><figure id="attachment_3502636" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502636" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3502636" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502636" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：战区》图片来源：动视</figcaption></figure><p>今年，玩家仍然无法避免在 Al Mazrah 或 Vondead 抢劫时可能触发的随机跳跃恐慌。还有一些独特的物品，例如寻血者手榴弹，可以通过热成像跟踪敌人。</p><p>此外，《Zombies Royale》将带着故事的转折回归。倒下的玩家不会去古拉格，而是会复活为僵尸，使他们有能力追捕以前的盟友。或者，他们可以收集特殊的注射器来治愈感染并再次成为人类。</p><p>随着比赛的进行，所有比赛的观众也将再次成为僵尸，动视建议玩家应该尝试由活人和不死玩家组成的小队来尝试获胜策略。</p><p>最后，第六季的新干员是阿尔·西蒙斯、阿鲁卡德·阿什·威廉姆斯、伊纳留斯、莉莉丝、骷髅、Spawn 和 V4L3RIA。伊纳留斯和莉莉丝跨界自<em>《暗黑破坏神 4》</em> ，而漫画人物艾尔·西蒙斯则获得了“烧毁的产卵”皮肤，象征着他向反派的转变。 </p><figure id="attachment_3502639" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502639" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3502639" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/call-of-duty-the-haunting-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502639" class="wp-caption-text"> 《使命召唤：战区》图片来源：动视</figcaption></figure><p><em>《使命召唤：战区</em>》第 6 季将于 9 月 27 日上线，《鬼魂》将于 10 月 17 日上线。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/ubisoft">育碧</a>透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-division-3-confirmed-will-be-produced-by-star-wars-outlaws-director-3502545"><em>《汤姆克兰西：全境封锁 3》</em>正在开发中</a>，并将由前两款游戏的创意总监负责。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/diablo-4s-lilith-is-coming-to-call-of-duty-3502610">《暗黑破坏神 4》的莉莉丝即